# Quick-start task runner (just — https://github.com/casey/just) — reusable library.
#
# Ships the full build-recipe vocabulary (RSS-3, #321): every INTERFACE target has
# a standard `just` recipe here — the one place recipes live. `recipe.py <t>`
# routes to `just <t>` via .claude/recipes.json. Placeholder bodies carry
# `# grimoire:placeholder` until wired; sync-deps/vendor-check delegate to the
# framework scripts. A library has no server to run and nothing to deploy, so its
# .claude/recipes.json declares `run`/`deploy` absent (advisory in
# grm-install-doctor); the recipes are still present as placeholders for uniformity.
# Authority: docs/design/justfile-standard-design.md +
# docs/grimoire/design/build-recipe-interface-design.md.

set shell := ["bash", "-uc"]

# build — compile the library.
build env="dev":
